thread.title: Treasury to Sell $97 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury to Sell $97 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. Treasury Department will auction $97 billion in securities next week, comprising $7 billion in new debt and $90 billion in previously sold debt. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Monday: $48 billion in 13-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Nov. 16, 2017, maturing May 17, 2018. Cusip number: T912796PG8.
